text_value: The 1D4 antibody was immobilized via standard amino coupling  on CM5 sensor surface to densities of 12-18 kRUs. Sensor surface is 10 min activated with 0.2 M EDC/ 0.05 M NHS mixture, antibody is contacted at 10 ug/ml in 10 mM sodium acetate buffer to reach required levels. Sensor surface is finally deactivated with 1 M ethanolamin, pH 8.0. A2A nanodsics are applied over 1D4 antibody surface to reach levels of 3000-6000 RUs.
